{
  "definitions": {},
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "http://example.com/root.json",
  "type": "object",
  "title": "The Root Schema",
  "required": [
    "id",
    "name",
    "type",
    "price",
    "shipping",
    "upc",
    "description",
    "manufacturer",
    "model",
    "url",
    "image",
    "updatedAt",
    "createdAt"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "id": {
      "$id": "#/properties/id",
      "type": "integer",
      "title": "The Id Schema",
      "default": 0,
      "examples": [
        9999699
      ]
    },
    "name": {
      "$id": "#/properties/name",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Name Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "Test product"
      ],
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "type": {
      "$id": "#/properties/type",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Type Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "test"
      ],
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "price": {
      "$id": "#/properties/price",
      "type": "integer",
      "title": "The Price Schema",
      "default": 0,
      "examples": [
        100
      ]
    },
    "shipping": {
      "$id": "#/properties/shipping",
      "type": "integer",
      "title": "The Shipping Schema",
      "default": 0,
      "examples": [
        3
      ]
    },
    "upc": {
      "$id": "#/properties/upc",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Upc Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "string"
      ],
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "description": {
      "$id": "#/properties/description",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Description Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "My short description"
      ],
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "manufacturer": {
      "$id": "#/properties/manufacturer",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Manufacturer Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "Demo"
      ],
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "model": {
      "$id": "#/properties/model",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Model Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "AA"
      ],
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "url": {
      "$id": "#/properties/url",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Url Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "myurl"
      ],
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "image": {
      "$id": "#/properties/image",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Image Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "path_to_my_png"
      ],
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "updatedAt": {
      "$id": "#/properties/updatedAt",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Updatedat Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "2019-02-13T10:23:18.630Z"
      ],
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "createdAt": {
      "$id": "#/properties/createdAt",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Createdat Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "2019-02-13T10:23:18.630Z"
      ],
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    }
  }
}
